/uploads/2024/01/pomodoro-sauce-ingredients-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/pomodoro-sauce-ingredients-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/pomodoro-sauce-ingredients-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/pomodoro-sauce-ingredients-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/pomodoro-sauce-ingredients-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/pomodoro-sauce-ingredients-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/pomodoro-sauce-ingredients.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-tips-amp-additions\"\u003eTips \u0026amp; Additions\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAs with any recipe with so few ingredients, the quality of those ingredients matter. If possible, use San Marzano tomatoes.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eFeel free to add more herbs beyond basil if you like, including parsley, thyme or even cilantro.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eI like to add a little red pepper flakes or cayenne to this sauce for heat. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eIf you want to use fresh (not canned) tomatoes, you can! Learn how to prepare and peel them in this \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/zesty-tomato-and-orange-sauce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003etomato and orange sauce\u003c/a\u003e recipe. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eIf you’re looking to add protein, you can add cooked Italian sausage or ground beef to your sauce.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/pomodoro-sauce/?tp_image_id=121770\" data-pin-title=\"Pomodoro Sauce (5 minute recipe!)\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-500x500.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%201200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-pomodoro-sauce.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-what-to-serve-pomodoro-sauce-with\"\u003eWhat to serve Pomodoro Sauce with:\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eI love to serve pasta with a meat and/or vegetable side dish or salad. Here are a few favorites. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/adventures-in-pasta-making/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eHomemade Pasta\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/air-fryer-meatballs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eAir Fryer Meatballs \u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/baked-chicken/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eBaked Chicken\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\